MODE erlang

ASPELL >=0.60.7

MAGIC /<noregex>/erl/escript
MAGIC /<noregex>/hrl

DESCRIPTION mode for checking Erlang code (.erl/.escript/.hrl) comments and string/binary/atom literals

FILTER url
FILTER context
OPTION clear-context-delimiters
OPTION add-context-delimiters <<" ">>
OPTION add-context-delimiters " "
OPTION add-context-delimiters ' '
OPTION add-context-delimiters % \0
